<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>VT 365 Diesel Engine - 2004 Model Year - CYLINDER HEAD AND VALVE TRAIN - Installation - Hydraulic Cam
        Follower
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="s26504.4.5" svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Hydraulic Cam Follower</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Clean hydraulic cam followers and roller follower guide. Use care to maintain roller
                follower identification and orientation.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Identify orientation of each cam follower and guide during assembly.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f2650484" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd03/d0303.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Installation of cam follower in guide</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lubricate and put each hydraulic cam follower in its respective roller follower guide.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650485" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd03/d0302.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Installation of cam followers and guide</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lubricate cam followers with clean engine oil and install cam followers in correct bores.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>See" High-pressure Oil Pump" section, for procedure to mount branch tube assembly over rear cam
                    follower guides.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install an M6 x 15 bolt with washer on roller follower guides (front guides only) and torque
                bolt to the standard value .
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
